clone

@Deprecated
public static java.lang.Object clone(java.lang.Object original)
Deprecated. As of release 2.0, replaced by deepClone(Object original)

Deep clones the Serializable objects in the current classloader. This method is slow and uses Object streams to clone Serializable objects. This method is now deprecated because of its inefficiency and the limitation to clone Serializable objects only. The use of deepClone or shallowClone is now recommended

original -
Returns:
